<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h2"> ODS Feed Manager Personal Use Case: News Monitoring</bridgehead>
<para>Individuals interested in discovering headline news based on a specific brand or keyword can use feeds to monitor news sources.</para>
<para>Online newspapers use feeds to to alert readers when new articles and content are available.
 The feed entry can be anything from sports to todays&#39; weather forecast.
 Depending on the feed source the News aggregators will include article summary or introduction and a link to the entire article.
 Readers can then ascertain if the article is of interest and read further or decide to read other articles, linked directly to to the publisher.</para>
